  .row.align-center.small-up-1.large-up-3.row--card-grid
    .column
      .card.drop
        .card-section
          h4.headline-5 HITRUST is how healthcare does business
          p The HITRUST Common Security Framework (CSF) has become the preferred way to prove compliance in healthcare. HITRUST certification helps establish and accelerate partnerships. If you plan to do business in healthcare at the speed of change, you need to be HITRUST CSF Certified.
    .column
      .card.drop
        .card-section
          h4.headline-5 Datica’s HITRUST CSF Certification gives you industry credibility overnight
          p Datica leads the industry with the first, most complete HIPAA compliant cloud infrastructure. Datica Managed Cloud is HITRUST CSF Certified on AWS, Microsoft Azure, IBM SoftLayer, and Rackspace, achieving the highest industry privacy and security standards across infrastructure providers.
    .column
      .card.drop
        .card-section
          h4.headline-5 You inherit Datica’s certification
          p HITRUST allows for inheritance, which means if you are planning to obtain your own CSF certification, you can inherit Datica’s certificate to shortcut 40% of the time and costs of the process.

